metadata.name: XCOPY-Inspired "summer.jpg" T-Shirt
metadata.description:
Created by Core3D, this digital T-Shirt collectible was inspired by the CC0 XCOPY art piece "summer.jpg" and adapted for oncyber by M0DAL. Like the XCOPY work it's based on, this T-shirt is by extension CC0.

As for the physical version--

Well. More details on that thoon...

Core3D is an online 3D design platform specializing in apparel. The platform's web-based editor gives anyone, anywhere, the ability to create high-end designs for physical and digital use. Web3 projects use Core3D to engage their audience, build IP and generate revenue through designs they create.
